  <description><![CDATA[<p>Enjoy the best of the Norwegian fjord’s glorious and diverse scenery in this exclusive 4-centre group tour. Designed as an excellent introduction to Norway for those wishing to see the spectacular fjords, mountains, glaciers and lakes in four contrasting destinations - from the historic city of <a data-udi="umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5}" title="Bergen">Bergen</a> to the serene Sognefjord, and from the glacier arms in <a data-udi="umb://document/14f6ab787ad2493ab23ce60aa9f14e6a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/14f6ab787ad2493ab23ce60aa9f14e6a}" title="Loen">Loen</a> to the Atlantic coast in <a data-udi="umb://document/4796d8535a46439d92020f8a158e7c03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4796d8535a46439d92020f8a158e7c03}" title="Alesund">Ålesund</a>. This tour gives you an insight into the ‘real’ Norway where even your transfers between resorts are spectacular scenic day trips.</p>
<p> </p>
