  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;"><strong>Bergen</strong> (2 nights) <a data-udi="umb://document/0d46aba9adc646f2afb1eeefe50bbc3f" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/bergen/augustin-hotel" title="Augustin Hotel">Augustin</a> ★★★+ <span>A friendly family-run hotel, beautifully decorated with a welcoming atmosphere and many special touches. Centrally situated which makes the harbour, fish market and Bryggen Wharf approximately a 3-4 minute walk (350m). This hotel is a great choice to explore this fascinating city, conveniently located to shops and a good selection of international restaurants.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;"><strong>Balestrand</strong> (3 nights) <a data-udi="umb://document/d26dcba440054402b9ccfe7166c1ad56" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/balestrand/kviknes-hotel" title="Kviknes Hotel">Kviknes</a> ★★★★<span>This wonderfully atmospheric historic dates back to 1752. Today with its modern amenities, main wing and attentive personal service it remains one of Fjord Norway’s best loved, family-run properties. The attractive original Swiss style wing radiates personality and soul, with an absolutely magnificent scenic fjord-side location and panoramic views across the Sognefjord.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;"><strong>Loen</strong> (3 nights) <a data-udi="umb://document/fbdb2d63e0f24d7fb8fbb7a20fdd9578" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/loen/alexandra-hotel" title="Alexandra Hotel">Alexandra</a> ★★★★+ <span>Built in 1884 the Alexandra is an intimate and truly special fifth generation family-run hotel steeped in tradition and set in the heart of this breathtakingly beautiful region. As one of Norway’s very best hotels, and is a favourite in our programme, it combines genuine hospitality, exceptional cuisine, gardens and extensive pool and spa facilities.</span></p>
<p style="margin: 0cm; margin-bottom: .0001pt;"><strong>Ålesund</strong> (3 nights) <a data-udi="umb://document/399112bca5344a2e8d6d9e81b1c02f28" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/norway/alesund/scandic-parken" title="Scandic Parken">Scandic Parken</a> ★★★★ <span>A classic city hotel located in the heart of Ålesund, just a few steps from the main street and 2 minutes' walk from the harbour. With a traditionally-decorated rooms, large public areas and light, pleasantly-decorated rooms, the Scandic is an excellent base in this Atlantic city. A buffet evening meal is included for tour guests on the first night of their stay, whilst a selection of traditional and international restaurants are on your doorstep for the rest of your stay - make sure you try the local bacalao!</span></p>]]></roomsDescription>
